name: cd\_immune
description: duration for which individuals stay immune after having contracted Covid-19

name: cd\_infectious\_true
description: time between infection and the onset of infectiousness

name: cd\_symptoms\_true
description: time until the onset of symptoms, can be indefinite, for individuals of age group $a$

name: cd\_symptoms\_false
description: duration of symptoms for symptomatic cases

name: cd\_needs\_icu\_true
description: time until an individual requires intensive care (given she has developed symptoms). The probability of and duration until requiring intensive care depends on the individual’s age group $a$

name: cd\_needs\_icu\_false
description: time until an individual recovers from requiring intensive care

name: cd\_dead\_true
description: time until an individual dies in intensive care. The probability of and duration until death depends on the individual’s age group $a$
